Actions.Text: AMEND AND RECOMMIT TO LOCAL GOVERNMENTS
AMEND AND RECOMMIT TO LOCAL GOVERNMENTS

Title: Authorizes the county of Suffolk to alienate certain lands used as parkland and to dedicate certain other lands as parklands
Summary: Authorizes the county of Suffolk to alienate certain lands used as parkland to Russel and Deana Galindo for the purpose of residential improvements and to dedicate certain other lands as parklands.
ActClause: AN ACT authorizing the county of Suffolk to alienate certain lands used as parkland and to dedicate certain other lands as parklands
